data.description: Sensational 4-bedroom, open concept floor plan with multiple living areas, high vaulted ceilings in main living and main bedroom.  Garage has epoxy floor, screened garage door and metal shelving.  This is a beautiful home and beyond move in ready. See the home features attachment for the numerous upgrades. Centrally convenient location in desired gated community of Oak Chase.
